citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:47a -
12:17p on 18-Oct-16.
ACI Bartels knocked on the door of the house, honked the horn of the government owned vehicle, and called the
number on file. No contact was made at that time.
